org.daisy.common.priority

Class PrioritizableRunnable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.common.priority.PrioritizableRunnable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, Prioritizable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ForwardingPrioritableRunnable

    public class PrioritizableRunnable<T>
extends Object
implements Prioritizable<T>, Runnable
    A runnable that holds an associated priority. This priority may be computed somehow but it must allow to force it.
    This object also has a timestamp and relative waiting time.
